    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ancient Roman cast bronze coins, usually in the form of ingots, and in circulation before 300 BCE, preceding the aes grave.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
